Remake: Auron (FFX)
Weapon type: Greatsword
Crystal Color: Red
Spheres: B E E

Skill 1: Banishing Blade
 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
 Inflicts ATK Down (20%), DEF Down (20%), INT BRV Down (20%), and Max BRV Down (20%) on target for 3 turns.
 Uses: 5
15cp: Kotetsu
 +Increases BRV potency
 +Increases effects of all debuffs inflicted (+20%)
 +Extends the duration of all inflicted debuffs by 3 turns
c.55: Banishing Blade Extend
 +Adds 3 uses
 +Becomes a 5-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
 +Greatly increases total BRV potency
 +Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow
 +Combines all inflicted debuffs into [Full Break] debuff, and increases the effects by 10%
 +Turns BRV Attack to BRV Attack+ for 8 turns after use

[Full Break]: ATK Down (30%), DEF Down (30%), INT BRV Down (30%), Max BRV Down (30%)
              *All effects +20% when 35cp passive is equipped
BRV Attack+: 2-hit Melee BRV Attack
             Deals greater BRV damage against debuffed targets

Skill 2: Sentinel
 Gain BRV based on own DEF (100%).
 Grants [Sentinel] to self for 4 turns.
 Uses: 3
35cp: Riot Blade
 +Increases BRV gain based on DEF (+100%)
 +Increases DEF Up effect of [Sentinel] (+100%)
 +Increases BRV Damage Reduction effect of [Sentinel] (+10%)
 +Extends base duration of [Sentinel] by 4 turns.
 +Grants ATK Up (40%) to self for 8 turns
c.60: Sentinel Extend
 +Adds 2 uses
 +Extends BRV gain based on own DEF to party
 +Multiplies own BRV by 1.4 before a 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
 +Allows for 120% Gained BRV overflow
 +Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow
 +Turns HP Attack to HP Attack+ for 8 turns after use
 
[Sentinel]: DEF Up (100%), BRV Damage Reduction (20%)
            Covers ST BRV/HP damage for allies
HP Attack+: 1-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
            Grants BRV to party based on (20% of) HP damage dealt
            Deals greater BRV damage against debuffed targets

EX: Conqueror
 +Equips EX ability Tornado
5-hit AoE Melee BRV+HP attack.
Deals 100% HP damage to all targets.
Grants [Bushido] to self for 8 turns.
 Recast: Slow
  -LB1: Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Increases recast speed of Tornado by 20%
  -LB3: Inflicts Melee Resistance Down on all targets for 6 turns
 EX+: Greatly increases BRV potency
      Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow
      Deals greater BRV damage against debuffed targets
  -LB1: Raises own ATK (50%) and Max BRV (80%)
  -LB2: At Quest start:
        Grants [Sentinel], ATK Up (40%) to self for 8 turns
        Fills Recast gauge to MAX
  -LB3: Becomes a 5-hit AoE Melee BRV+HP attack, triggered twice.
        Deals 100% HP damage to all targets.
        Turns [Melee Resistance Down] into a framed debuff, and extends its base duration by 2 turns.
        Deals greater BRV damage against debuffed targets.
        Turns BRV Attack, BRV Attack+ to BRV Attack++ while [Bushido] is active
        Turns HP Attack, HP Attack+ to HP Attack++ while [Bushido] is active

[Bushido]: Max BRV Up (60%), Stolen BRV Overflow Limit Up (30%)
BRV Attack++: BRV Attack+: 3-hit Melee BRV attack
              Deals greater BRV damage against debuffed targets
HP Attack+: 2-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
            Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow
            Grants BRV to party based on (30% of) HP damage dealt
            Deals greater BRV damage against debuffed targets

LD: Heaven's Cloud
 +Equips LD ability Dragon Fang
4-hit AoE Melee BRV+HP attack, triggered twice.
Resets BREAK status on all targets after first HP attack.
Inflicts [Threatened] on all targets for 3 turns.
 Uses: 3
  -LB1: Raises ATK (30%), DEF (80%)
        Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Raises ATK (30%), DEF (80%)
        Extends base duration of [Threatened] by 3 turns
  -LB3: Raises ATK (30%), DEF (80%)
        Adds 1 use
Board Passive: LD Extend
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Increases own BRV by (20% of) HP damage dealt after first HP attack
 +Delays all targets by 1 turn after last HP attack

[Threatened]: BRV Damage Dealt Down (50%)
              HP Damage Dealt Down (50%)
